// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1100 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e0c12e1f-5528-553d-8070-c584b143140d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
